  <\question>
    解方程

    <\equation*>
      x<rsup|4>+<frac|4a|a-1>x<rsup|3>+<frac|6a|a-1>x<rsup|2>+<frac|4a|a-1>x+1=0
    </equation*>

    <\answer*>
      两侧同时除以<math|x<rsup|2>>，从而

      <\equation*>
        <around*|(|x<rsup|>+<frac|1|x<rsup|>>|)><rsup|2>+<frac|4a|a-1><around*|(|x+<frac|1|x>|)>+<frac|6a|a-1>-2=0
      </equation*>

      令<math|y=x+<frac|1|x>>

      <\equation*>
        y<rsup|2>+<frac|4a|a-1>y+<frac|6a|a-1>-2=0
      </equation*>

      解得

      <\equation*>
        y=-<frac|2a|a-1>\<pm\><frac|<sqrt|2<around*|(|a+1|)>>|a-1>
      </equation*>

      注意到<math|x<rsup|2>-x y+1=0>,解得

      <\equation*>
        x=<frac|y\<pm\><sqrt|y<rsup|2>-4>|2>
      </equation*>
    </answer*>
  </question>

